# SafePathAI-SafePath AI

AI-Powered Disaster Response Agent built with Gemini and Google Cloud Agent Builder.

Overview

SafePath AI helps people prepare for and respond to disasters such as floods, cyclones, and severe weather events.

Instead of only showing alerts, SafePath AI creates personalized action plans, recommends shelters, generates emergency checklists, and helps users stay informed during emergencies.

Features

- Real-time disaster alerts
- Risk assessment
- Shelter discovery
- Personalized evacuation plans
- Emergency preparedness checklist
- Family notification workflow
- Disaster history tracking

Built With

- Python
- Google Cloud Agent Builder
- Gemini
- MongoDB
- MongoDB MCP Server
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- GitHub

How It Works

1. User enters location.
2. Agent checks disaster conditions.
3. Risk level is calculated.
4. Nearby shelters are identified.
5. Personalized evacuation instructions are generated.
6. Emergency checklist is created.
7. Family notification workflow is triggered.

